  <h2>The Autopilot story</h2>

  <p>Hi, I'm Matt. I run a number of online stores and know how time-consuming
  it is to pick, pack and ship all of your orders out.</p>

  <p>I found that existing order fulfilment companies were not suitable for my
  small eCommerce stores. They were difficult to set up, confusing, inflexible,
  and expensive.</p>

  <p>Disappointed, I resumed shipping my own orders and soon realised that
  there must be other online stores in the same position as I was. By storing
  and shipping their stock, I could offer the service that I was looking for.
  And so AutoPilot was born.</p>

  <p>Since we're a small business, we offer the flexibility, personal service,
  and care that you can't get from a large 3rd party logistics (3PL) company.
  We know how important it is for orders to be picked, packed and shipped
